          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add 60g <span class=\"text-danger\">[120g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> curry powder</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 80ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[160ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and mix thoroughly until combined – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a separate plate</p>",
